<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أخرجه مسلم <span class="c2">(١٣٩٠)</span> والنسائي <span class="c2">(٢/ ٢٩)</span> وفي <span class="c1">"الكبرى"</span> <span class="c2">(٧٧٤ و ٤٢٨٩)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
